680
00:43:22,519 --> 00:43:25,639
King, Ashile Tribe... Ashile Tribe is mounting an attack.

681
00:43:29,759 --> 00:43:30,919
Which one?

682
00:43:30,920 --> 00:43:33,679
The troops leading the charge hang out the flags of Eagle and Bear Division.

683
00:43:33,680 --> 00:43:34,480
Eagle Division?

684
00:43:35,640 --> 00:43:36,720
Eagle Division is here.

685
00:43:37,640 --> 00:43:39,040
That'd make things much easier now.

